Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Main】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正直老人号离开了艾斯塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所幸其后没有被泰坦尼亚发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星巴格休
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星バルガシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利逃到了巴格休
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前也来过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休地处边境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚在此处的势力应该不强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要躲开泰坦尼亚 这里最合适不过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能一味逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能在这里出现转机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 有个人想请提督见见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当地反泰坦尼亚势力的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道对方底细
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但主动拜托的话 对方应该会帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就经由其它渠道和此处的流星旗军联系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反泰坦尼亚和流星旗军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这下应该能热闹点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1465,850)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}沙漠之鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗舰队和正直老人号的交战记录到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此进行分析之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算出了正直老人号的逃走路线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的去向是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休·卡嘉诺特一带
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚势力尚未触及的空域吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来对方的逃走路线也经过一番计算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问如何处置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上向各个星球派遣搜查队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令驻留军同意搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此失陪 大总统阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一场卓有成果的谈判 谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}埃尔伯特·卡纳库大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルベルト・カナック大統領
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除去泰坦尼亚驻军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让对方同意了全部条件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官佩服之至
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于驻军的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一开始就不认为对方会同意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不认同泰坦尼亚统治的星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点也是最招人反感的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 巴格休星也早晚会成为问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你新的赴任地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说哲力胥阁下向巴格休·卡嘉诺特方面派遣了方修利搜查队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿果然很着急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿不会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密卿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的坐船送你去巴格休吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那不是提督先生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我这边喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有约了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你喜欢那种类型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是沾花惹草的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里喝茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方的联络员会带我们去沙漠里的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然的邂逅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是场美妙的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 已经联系上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个座位有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的是的 不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是长得有一点点像…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 方修利来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是我们的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里等于是反泰坦尼亚的巢穴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 大家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休这样讨厌泰坦尼亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那些家伙最近在镇上到处转
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追 快追
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用看店了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是联络员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然出了点意外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但从那边可以逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我方特务舰正彻底清查他的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把巴格休方圆二十里拍上一张卫星照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现他就只是时间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们一旦发现 马上降落到巴格休
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们本队也向巴格休进发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这样会侵害到巴格休的主权…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 告诉巴格休政府
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚的敌人由泰坦尼亚自己抓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若敢妄加干预 小心会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}塔鲁哈利沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}タルハリ砂漠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的首领就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的藏身处还真偏僻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利还真是胆小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是单枪匹马挑战泰坦尼亚的男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对方把我捧起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让对方尽量捧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然岂不是很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不爽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1463,923)\fad(500,500)}伊文·卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1463,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}イブン・カシム
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊文·卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚好像出了点情况 对不住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 多谢你们救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请恕我单刀直入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的船上有通讯接进来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平安回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为正直老人号开到了附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 想请提督暂时留在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是沙漠正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚还是想和你们合流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚已经来了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 有情况随时联系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方也想与贵方合作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利提督就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道反泰坦尼亚派值不值得信任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但朋友还是越多越好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这个星球上的流星旗军也不少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能借我几艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个万一的时候就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张椅子对您来说还是太大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看来是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 法尔的赴任地好像出了点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 据说在巴格休星发现了方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头疼 看来他还得过几天才能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好空气 活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没出息 已经喘粗气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个洞窟让人呼吸困难耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里据说是百万年前火山熔岩流过来形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知深处通往何处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也从百万年前就恨着泰坦尼亚 住在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但恨着泰坦尼亚倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种年轻姑娘是为了替父母报仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲是个才华横溢的钢琴家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但被和泰坦尼亚有关的竞争对手抢去了机会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的首领也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个医生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时失去了妻儿和医院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人也或多或少和泰坦尼亚有点仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要和泰坦尼亚作对？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想说的话就当我没说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 勉强说来 是为了蛋包饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能平安离开这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就给我做蛋包饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(807,923)\fad(500,500)}泰坦尼亚特务舰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(807,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}タイタニア特務艦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚的特务舰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 在沙漠中央发现生命反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下降途中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了方修利的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的鼠辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从巢里钻出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用等本队到达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要抓活的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被泰坦尼亚的特务舰发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也和博士联络过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵力居然如此惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须撑到正直老人号赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这里不是泰坦尼亚的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可以随便动武吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我也没用啊 去问哲力胥阁下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷达上有反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是巴格休政府保安部队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本地动武属于违法行为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是对主权的重大侵害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上解除武装…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚只服从泰坦尼亚的上级指示
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方不打算撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知地面部队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始突击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一艘小艇果然派不上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的枪法有限呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 不开枪就只有死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗视装置是为了捕捉目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击也有所顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 对方还不打算杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道你是不是方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告各冲要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始投掷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面部队的损伤率
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14% 不 达到15%了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不需要生擒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以连洞窟一并破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损害继续增大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 这样下去恐怕会全军覆没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了 你真是方修利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 我差点忘了问救命恩人的大名了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}雪拉芬·库帕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}セラフィン・クーパーズ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪拉芬·库帕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我雪拉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪拉 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不知道对方的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还拜托她做蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话说得真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若没出息的方修利能用计打败他们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就给你做蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 是援军
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单凭这艘船行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一对一应该行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在博士赶来之前 我们得撑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休星的战斗此刻刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它将静静演变为动摇泰坦尼亚治世的一场大战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.50,0:24:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是和我同甘共苦的家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.94,0:24:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上承载着在卡萨比安卡的种种回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.47,0:24:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正直老人号虽然平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.21,0:24:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又如此可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(607,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}正直老人


